Package org.jasig.portlet.courseschedule.model

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Semester
    A Semester is generally a bean made up of the Season and the corresponding year.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Course
    Simple bean to describe basic course information: title, number and section.
    CourseMeeting
    CourseMeeting represents a regularly occurring course event.
    Grade
    Grade represents a received final grade in an individual course.
    MeetingLocation
    MeetingLocation represents the location of a scheduled meeting.
    StudentCourseRegistration
    StudentCourseRegistration contains all the pertinant information to be displayed in the class schedule shown in the degree progress portlet.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Season
    Season is an enum representing the seasons of the year, which are generally used by academic institutions to designate semesters.
